 nećemo spaviti prije braka.

2092
00:55:56,100 --> 00:55:57,240
 Odlično, čestitam ti.

2093
00:55:57,240 --> 00:55:58,880
 Ok, šta smijemo raditi?

2094
00:55:59,700 --> 00:56:00,960
 Ja kažem imanta, dobro,

2095
00:56:00,960 --> 00:56:01,900
